1
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,000
Uncle Zhao.

2
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,280
Madam.

3
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,640
Have you seen Long'er?

4
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:03,040
I went to her room just now but didn't see her.

5
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,600
Madam.

6
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:05,120
To develop black tea,

7
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,780
Miss found a new tea workshop.

8
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,360
She goes out early every morning.

9
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,020
She's been working very hard.

10
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,160
I made a new dress for her.

11
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,960
I wanted her to try it on as soon as possible,

12
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,020
so I could alter it.

13
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,040
Then I'll just go find her at the new tea workshop.

14
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,079
Yes, Madam.

15
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,040
Miss!

16
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:30,880
Something bad happened!

17
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,320
The clan elders are at the council hall

18
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,360
holding a clan meeting.

19
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,020
Please go there immediately.

20
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,640
Madam has already been invited by them.

21
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,440
I'm afraid...

22
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,620
Afraid of what?

23
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:41,040
I'm afraid things are not looking good.

24
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:47,520
Hu Linglong.

25
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,770
I have a bad feeling about this.

26
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,040
They summoned you to the council hall

27
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,370
and must be up to no good.

28
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,079
I know.

29
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:57,120
But since they're holding a clan meeting,

30
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,640
something major must have happened to the Hu family.

31
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:01,160
Even if it's ominous,

32
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:03,000
we can only play it by ear.

33
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,800
Don't be afraid.

34
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,680
You are now the head of the Hu family.

35
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,320
They wouldn't dare do anything to you.

36
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,560
Besides, I'm here.

37
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:10,680
When necessary,

38
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,540
I will help you.

39
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,640
Let's go.

40
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:21,560
The head of the family has arrived!

41
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:22,600
Mother!

42
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:25,970
Are you alright?

43
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:26,840
I'm fine.

44
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,280
Elders,

45
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:34,880
why did you summon me here today,

46
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:35,800
and for what matter?

47
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,640
Hu Linglong,

48
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,050
do you plead guilty?

49
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,280
What crime have I committed?

50
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:44,320
Hmph!

51
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,250
You still have the nerve to ask?

52
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,800
You've been the head of the family for less than a month,

53
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:54,320
and you've almost ruined the Hu family's business!

54
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:57,120
You've almost made the Hu family lose all its face!

55
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,720
Are you worthy of the trust

56
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:00,440
the entire Hu family has in you?

57
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,300
Are you worthy of your ancestors?

58
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:03,640
Hmph!

59
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:08,000
Are you talking about the tea business with the British merchants?

60
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,800
What other business could it be?

61
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:10,960
Hu Linglong,

62
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:12,680
you know very well

63
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:15,840
that more than half of our Hu family's tea business

64
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:18,320
is in cooperation with the British merchants.

65
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,000
But you

66
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:22,360
have offended all the British merchants now.

67
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,130
They are now colluding with each other

68
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,160
and have canceled all our subsequent

69
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,600
orders.

70
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:32,090
You handle accounts and cargo contracts all day,

71
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,720
you should know better than I do.

72
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:37,680
Elders,

73
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,280
half a month ago I was indeed at the tea garden

74
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,920
and had a dispute with the British merchants.

75
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,800
But there was a reason.

76
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,920
They caused trouble and beat people up.

77
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,800
Foolish!

78
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:48,300
You still shouldn't have offended them!

79
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,280
If our tea farmers

80
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:52,600
are bullied a bit,

81
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,520
we just need to console them.

82
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,159
Now,

83
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,920
by offending the British merchants,

84
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,840
we won't even have food to eat.

85
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,480
Do you think

86
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,000
your momentary bravado

87
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,680
at the tea factory

88
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,500
is really for the good of the tea farmers?

89
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,440
Clan Elder.

90
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,400
I understand the reasoning.

91
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,000
But the foreign merchants keep forcing the prices down,

92
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,600
and the tea farmers can't make ends meet.

93
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,160
Nowadays, when foreign tea is imported,

94
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,880
they only need to pay

95
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,520
a meager transit tax.

96
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,840
Yet our tea farmers have to bear

97
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,120
the heavy Likin tax.

98
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:21,800
If this continues,

99
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:24,200
it's not a long-term solution, Clan Elder.

100
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,400
Long-term solution?

101
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,130
Hu Linglong,

102
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:29,120
then I must consult you.

103
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:31,720
What is a long-term solution?

104
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:33,820
Clan Elder.

105
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:36,960
The reason Keemun black tea is constantly suppressed in price by British merchants

106
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,240
is not just because Indians and Ceylon people

107
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,360
stole our tea seeds to study and copy.

108
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:44,000
It is even more because, with the support of British merchants,

109
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:46,860
they have already begun standardized production.

110
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,320
Nowadays, Keemun black tea must urgently improve

111
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,920
to find a way out, Clan Elder.

112
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:51,800
Hmph.

113
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,159
Indian

114
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,100
and Ceylon teas

115
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:56,280
have always been low-end products.

116
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,159
Those foreigners

117
00:05:57,159 --> 00:05:59,220
try every means to steal our tea seeds

118
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,490
and our techniques.

119
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:01,560
This

120
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,800
is the best proof.

121
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,280
Oh.

122
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,200
You old fogeys of the Hu family

123
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,360
are really stubborn

124
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,620
and highly conceited.

125
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,640
It's no wonder that Keemun black tea

126
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,440
is in such a predicament today.

127
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,520
Times have changed,

128
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,860
no need to say more.

129
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:20,540
Clan Elder.

130
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,460
The top priority right now

131
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:24,080
is how to deal with

132
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:26,120
the canceled British orders.

133
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,040
If those teas

134
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:30,800
in the warehouse are not sold in time,

135
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,600
the loss to our Hu family

136
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,040
will be immeasurable.

137
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:37,200
It will be irreversible, Clan Elder.

138
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,080
Yes.

139
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,330
Hu Linglong.

140
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:46,440
Let me ask you.

141
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:49,040
After the British merchants canceled the orders,

142
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,360
how much of our Hu family's tea

143
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:53,080
is still stuck in the warehouse?

144
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,480
Around 220 piculs.

145
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,600
Ah.

146
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,440
Then tell me,

147
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,360
if these teas

148
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:08,280
are not sold to the British,

149
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,440
is there

150
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,600
any other market?

151
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,240
Come on,

152
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,400
tell me.

153
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,020
Not for now.

154
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,040
Hmph.

155
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:25,920
Alas.

156
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:31,620
This is bad.

157
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,800
I have to find a way to help her.

158
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,600
Hu Linglong,

159
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,240
if you have no solution,

160
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,120
I do.

161
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,440
Tell them

162
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:38,400
Keemun black tea can take this opportunity

163
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,880
to change its business strategy,

164
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:41,640
producing medium and low-grade tea.

165
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:43,120
Opening up the local market

166
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,850
can solve the current dilemma.

167
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:46,800
These old fogeys know nothing.

168
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,360
Tell them quickly.

169
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:50,280
I understand.

170
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,760
Elders,

171
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,520
I have a plan

172
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:54,400
to solve the Hu family's urgent need.

173
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:54,880
Oh?

174
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,640
Let's hear it.

175
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,280
We can upgrade and improve the tea,

176
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:03,760
and then make the hoarded tea into tea bricks,

177
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:05,840
to supply the escort agencies and docks.

178
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:08,160
Keemun black tea is of premium quality, we can sell it at a small profit but quick turnover,

179
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,640
maintain our foundation, expand our market,

180
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,720
and survive by volume.

181
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,600
Absurd!

182
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,480
The tea produced by our Hu family

183
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:15,140
has always been for royal use,

184
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:17,520
sold only to high officials and nobles.

185
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,600
By doing this,

186
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,720
you are simply insulting the reputation

187
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,000
of our Hu family's tea.

188
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,440
Yes.

189
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,640
What Wenyi just said is very true.

190
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,040
But...

191
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:29,490
Hu Linglong,

192
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,040
let me ask you,

193
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,880
these 212 piculs of tea

194
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,059
are worth nearly ten thousand taels.

195
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:37,120
How are you

196
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,159
going to settle this account?

197
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:39,840
How are you

198
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,409
going to fill this hole?

199
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:45,380
It's all because of your momentary impulse.

200
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,800
Do you know how many people you have harmed?

201
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,080
As the head of the family,

202
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,280
you cannot shirk your responsibility.

203
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:53,760
Elders,

204
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,400
I think

205
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:57,120
it's better to let her go to the foreign firm

206
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,840
and commit suicide to apologize.

207
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,480
After all,

208
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,520
she provoked someone she shouldn't have,

209
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,920
and ending up like this

210
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,520
is what she deserves.

211
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:11,760
Hu Linglong,

212
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:14,720
did you hear

213
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,920
what Dabao just said?

214
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,240
Did you?

215
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:24,160
This Hu Sanshan is also an old fool.

216
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:26,160
You Hu family people are all wicked.

217
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,360
Why should you sacrifice your life for the wicked?

218
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,360
Those Brits,

219
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,880
none of them are good.

220
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,480
You don't even know what's coming next.

221
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,640
Especially this Hu Wenyi,

222
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:35,000
he just wants to kill you.

223
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,360
You absolutely cannot agree with him.

224
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,360
I can see it.

225
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,840
He just wants to be the head of the family.

226
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,900
How can he be the head if you don't die?

227
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:47,520
They simply leave us no way out.

228
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,760
Miss,

229
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:50,040
you protect us so much,

230
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,280
we must support you.

231
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:52,880
Elders,

232
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,640
I understand.

233
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,240
Long'er,

234
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,160
don't be silly.

235
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:04,880
Hu Linglong,

236
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:06,240
you must not be foolish.

237
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,880
Even if you do as they say

238
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,440
and apologize to the British merchants,

239
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:11,400
even if you take your own life at their door,

240
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,120
they will only

241
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,440
intensify their bullying of the tea farmers

242
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,680
and suppress the Hu family.

243
00:10:14,680 --> 00:10:15,480
Tell us,

244
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:17,130
stop stalling for time.

245
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,000
Elders,

246
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,800
I am not stalling on purpose.

247
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:22,040
There is something I want to make clear.

248
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:24,480
If I go to the foreign firm to commit suicide today,

249
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:26,410
it's not because I think I am wrong,

250
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:29,360
but because I don't want the tea farmers to be implicated because of me,

251
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:31,560
and I don't want the Hu family's business to be ruined by my hands.

252
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:32,520
That's all.

253
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,000
Hu Linglong,

254
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,120
you can't do anything stupid.

255
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,480
You can't agree to their terms!

256
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,280
Hu Linglong,

257
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,280
answer me!

258
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,120
Hu Linglong.

259
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,720
So you mean

260
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,400
you are willing to die?

261
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:47,520
I...

262
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:49,360
Things have come to this,

263
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,120
I have no choice but to take a risk.

264
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:53,040
Hu Linglong,

265
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:54,040
you can't die.

266
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,200
If you die,

267
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:57,530
the century-old Keemun black tea will...

268
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:12,680
Hu Linglong.

269
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,240
I don't care about the secrets of heaven,

270
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,900
I must save Hu Linglong today.

271
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,640
I am the future

272
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:24,440
black tea

273
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,160
heir.

274
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,240
Qiao Xin,

275
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,320
didn't we have an agreement

276
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:35,640
that you can't occupy my body as you please?

277
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:37,500
My soul seems to be out of control.

278
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,520
Hu Linglong,

279
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:40,570
stop playing the fool here.

280
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:41,760
Don't think that

281
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,160
we will let you off lightly.

282
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:43,800
Tell us,

283
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,720
when are you going to the foreign firm

284
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,960
to confess and commit suicide?

285
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:47,290
Hmph.

286
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:48,960
Why should I go to the foreign firm

287
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,680
and commit suicide to apologize?

288
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:51,160
You!

289
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,360
What?

290
00:11:53,560 --> 00:11:54,480
Qiao Xin,

291
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,520
sacrificing me alone can end this.

292
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:57,720
This is my body,

293
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,180
don't interfere anymore.

294
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:01,120
Hu Linglong.

295
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:02,520
Stand still.

296
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:07,280
I didn't expect you to be so capricious

297
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,200
and stubborn.

298
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:10,560
Then don't blame the Hu family

299
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:12,220
for not showing you any mercy.

300
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:12,800
Elders,

301
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,760
that was not my intention just now.

302
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:15,480
I...

303
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:17,360
You mean

304
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,840
you are willing to die?

305
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,450
Why should I be willing?

306
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,120
You!

307
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:27,760
Elders,

308
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:29,000
She,

309
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,040
she is making a fool out of us!

310
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,800
It's best to leave this place of trouble first.

311
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,480
Elder, I am feeling unwell today.

312
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:36,960
Maybe another day.

313
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:37,890
Trying to leave?

314
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,160
Stop her!

315
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,930
Why am I back here again?

316
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,520
Hu Linglong.

317
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,360
The clan meeting is not over yet.

318
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,160
You can't just leave as you please.

319
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:01,020
What a scandal!

320
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:03,240
If you refuse to apologize to the British merchant,

321
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:03,640
fine.

322
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:05,800
Now we are facing an imminent crisis of unsalable tea.

323
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:06,600
The Elder and I

324
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:09,080
have discussed marrying you off to the Zhang family.

325
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:09,880
At this point,

326
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,920
you have to agree to this matter,

327
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:13,380
whether you want to or not.

328
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,000
No.

329
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:15,160
No.

330
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,800
I will never marry into the Zhang family.

331
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:17,160
You!

332
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:19,800
Hu Linglong,

333
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:20,600
I've said it,

334
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,080
once spoken,

335
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,240
it's settled.

336
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:24,600
You will marry,

337
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,960
whether you want to or not.
